mil.nga.giat.geowave.store.dimension

Class LongitudeField

  • java.lang.Object
    • mil.nga.giat.geowave.store.dimension.SpatialField
      • mil.nga.giat.geowave.store.dimension.LongitudeField
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    NumericDimensionDefinition, Persistable, DimensionField<GeometryWrapper>

    public class LongitudeField
extends SpatialField
    This field can be used as a EPSG:4326 longitude dimension within GeoWave. It can utilize JTS geometry as the underlying spatial object for this dimension.
